pageData.devheader: A fundamental  course  in  Web  Development  utilizing  contemporary  standards,  methods,  and tools  for  students  to  develop  skills  in  creating  and  deploying  web-based  content. Students learn development concepts spanning markup and programming languages and libraries, local and hosted environments, versioning control systems, and development tools.
pageData.trone: DevDocs, W3CSchools, CodeAcademy, Content Delivery Networks, Documentation, Templates
